-- Lufthansa’s IT Unit Seeks Outside Sales Boost, Handelsblatt Says
-- B y   A l e x   W e b b
-- 2012-03-22T06:12:03Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-22/lufthansa-s-it-unit-seeks-outside-sales-boost-handelsblatt-says.html
Deutsche Lufthansa AG (LHA) ’s information
technology unit, Lufthansa Systems, is seeking to increase the
proportion of revenue it receives from outside the company to
more than half, from the current 40 percent,  Handelsblatt 
reported, citing Stefan Hansen, who heads the unit.  To contact the reporter on this story:
